---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
const title = "Lingoda Review 2026: The Pros and Cons of Language Marathons | LearnEnglish.Life";
const description = "Is the Lingoda Sprint worth it? We review Lingoda's English courses, class structure, and intensive learning programs.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-neutral-950 min-h-screen">
<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Review · Updated April 2026</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Lingoda Review: Is the Sprint Worth It?</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400">Lingoda is famous for its "Sprint" challenges where you can get your money back. But beyond the marketing, how good is the actual teaching?</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-500">8.0</div>
      <div>
        <div class="font-bold text-white">Our Score</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Best for structured group learning</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-neutral-300">Lingoda offers a structured, CEFR-aligned curriculum that is perfect for students who want a "real school" experience online. The group classes are small and interactive.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">How Lingoda Works</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">Lingoda offers small group classes (3-5 students) and 1-on-1 lessons. All teachers are native-level speakers. You follow a set curriculum based on your level (A1 to C1), and you can download the lesson materials in advance.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">The Lingoda Sprint</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">The Sprint is Lingoda's most popular feature. If you take a class every day (or every other day) for two months and follow all the rules, you can get 50% or 100% of your tuition back. It's a high-stakes way to stay motivated.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Pricing</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6">Lingoda uses a monthly subscription model. Group classes start at around $10-12 per class, while private lessons are around $25-30. The Sprint has its own pricing structure.</p>

  <div class="bg-emerald-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-center mt-12">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready for a Challenge?</h3>
    <p class="text-emerald-100 mb-6">Join the next Lingoda Sprint and master English.</p>
    <a href="https://www.lingoda.com/" class="inline-block bg-white text-emerald-600 font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-100 transition">Visit Lingoda</a>
  </div>

    <aside class="mt-12 mb-4 p-6 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Compare with other platforms</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-base">
        <li><a href="/reviews/see-guru/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>See Guru</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">3 free 1-on-1 lessons with real teachers</span></a></li>
        <li><a href="/reviews/italki/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>iTalki</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Largest tutor marketplace, 10M+ learners</span></a></li>
        <li><a href="/reviews/preply/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>Preply</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Structured plans with certified teachers</span></a></li>
        <li><a href="/reviews/cambly/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300"><strong>Cambly</strong> <span class="text-slate-400 font-normal">Unlimited talk time with native speakers</span></a></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-slate-700 text-sm text-slate-300">
        New here? Start with our <a href="/blog/how-long-to-learn-english/" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">CEFR reality check</a> to see how many hours your target really takes.
      </p>
    </aside>

  </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
